com.bandyer.android_sdk.call

Interface CallUIObserver


  • public CallUIObserver

    This class represent a call UI observer which will be notified when a call activity event has occurred.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onActivityDestroyed(Call call, java.lang.ref.WeakReference<androidx.appcompat.app.AppCompatActivity> activity)
      This function will be called when the call UI has been destroyed and hidden.
      void onActivityError(Call call, java.lang.ref.WeakReference<androidx.appcompat.app.AppCompatActivity> activity, CallException error)
      This function will be called when in the call UI has occurred an error.
      void onActivityStarted(Call call, java.lang.ref.WeakReference<androidx.appcompat.app.AppCompatActivity> activity)
      This function will be called when the call UI has been created&shown.
